snippet.title: Final Gear - Official Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Do you remember what the world used to look like?

But now...

The life, that once flourishing here is now diminishing. 

The surviving humanity is facing the most crucial challenge.

How will humanity fight for its survival this time?

[Final Gear] is coming soon. Stay tuned for the latest info at:
